<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cho Yeonjae | Portfolio</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f12;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      width: 700px;
      height: 700px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,183,197,0.18), transparent 70%);
      top: -250px;
      right: -200px;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,222,173,0.12), transparent 70%);
      bottom: -200px;
      left: -150px;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    nav {
      position: fixed;
      width: 100%;
      top: 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(15,15,18,0.7);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 24px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #ddd;
      transition: 0.3s;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: #ffb6c1;
    }

    section {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 120px 24px;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 4.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fff, #ffb6c1);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 700px;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: #cfcfcf;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .hero .tag {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      color: #ffb6c1;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .section-title::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -12px;
      width: 60%;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffb6c1, #ffd27f);
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }

    .about-card p {
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: #d5d5d5;
    }

    .skills {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .skill {
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      color: #f0f0f0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .project-card {
      margin-top: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(
        145deg,
        rgba(255,255,255,0.06),
        rgba(255,255,255,0.03)
      );
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 40px;
      transition: 0.4s;
    }

    .project-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(255,182,193,0.5);
    }

    .project-card h3 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .project-card .subtitle {
      color: #ffb6c1;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .project-card p {
      color: #d4d4d4;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .feature-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .feature-box h4 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .feature-box p {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      color: #cfcfcf;
    }

    .contact {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .contact p {
      color: #cfcfcf;
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .contact-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #111;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffb6c1, #ffd27f);
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      margin-top: 60px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }

      .about-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .nav-links {
        gap: 16px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .project-card {
        padding: 28px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="nav-container">
      <div class="logo">Cho Yeonjae</div>

      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="tag">Fine Art Student · SKKU</div>

    <h1>Cho<br>Yeonjae</h1>

    <p>
      I love arts and desserts.
      I want to eat all of the delicious desserts in the world —
      but first, in Korea.
      <br><br>
      I explore how design, culture, and data can come together through
      interactive visual storytelling and creative digital experiences.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-card">
        <p>
          Hello! I'm Cho Yeonjae, a Fine Art student at Sungkyunkwan University.
          My interests are centered around visual culture, creative technology,
          interactive media, and dessert aesthetics.
          <br><br>
          I enjoy transforming personal interests into meaningful digital projects.
          Through design and data visualization, I aim to create experiences that
          are both visually engaging and culturally expressive.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom:20px;">Skills & Tools</h3>

        <div class="skills">
          <div class="skill">HTML/CSS</div>
          <div class="skill">Python</div>
          <div class="skill">Streamlit</div>
          <div class="skill">Plotly</div>
          <div class="skill">Folium</div>
          <div class="skill">Pandas</div>
          <div class="skill">Creative Coding</div>
          <div class="skill">Data Visualization</div>
          <div class="skill">UI Design</div>
          <div class="skill">GitHub Pages</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="projects">
    <h2 class="section-title">Featured Project</h2>

    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Sweet Spots Korea</h3>

      <div class="subtitle">
        Interactive Dessert Cafe Map & Analytics Dashboard
      </div>

      <p>
        Korea's dessert cafe culture is one of the most visually creative
        and emotionally expressive scenes in the world.
        However, there are very few public tools that organize cafes
        by dessert type and regional characteristics.
        <br><br>
        Sweet Spots Korea transforms real cafe data into an interactive
        cultural atlas where users can discover dessert cafes by category,
        rating, city, and price range.
      </p>

      <div class="skills">
        <div class="skill">Streamlit</div>
        <div class="skill">Plotly</div>
        <div class="skill">Folium</div>
        <div class="skill">Pandas</div>
        <div class="skill">Google Maps API</div>
        <div class="skill">Kakao Local API</div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-grid">

        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Type-filtered Map</h4>
          <p>
            Color-coded dessert cafe markers with ratings,
            signature menus, and pricing information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Interactive Dashboard</h4>
          <p>
            Dynamic filters and synchronized charts that update live
            based on user selections.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Data Visualization</h4>
          <p>
            Scatter plots, donut charts, heatmaps,
            and analytics designed with dessert-inspired aesthetics.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Cultural Mapping</h4>
          <p>
            A creative archive of Korean dessert culture
            visualized through data and design.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="contact">
    <h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>

    <p>
      Interested in art, creative coding, desserts,
      or collaborative projects?
      <br>
      Feel free to connect with me.
    </p>

    <a class="contact-btn" href="mailto:your_email@example.com">
      Say Hello
    </a>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2026 Cho Yeonjae · Built with GitHub Pages
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
